nodes.text: Radorm was a Jedi Master of the Jedi Order, who attended Initiate Trials that were held underwater.
Radorm was first mentioned in the audiobook Dooku: Jedi Lost, written by Cavan Scott and published in 2019. The spelling of Radorm's name was given in the script of the audiobook.
